roperty sources, and a built-in .props/.properties parser. No external service, Docker image, environment variable, system property, or extra Maven dependency is required before useful coverage can be generated.\",\n  \"deterministic_setup\": [],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"The README's common YAML/JSON/HOCON examples require optional format modules such as hoplite-yaml or hoplite-hocon, but those are not required to exercise hoplite-core itself; generated tests should avoid choosing non-core file formats unless they also add the matching optional module.\",\n    \"The version jump from 2.9.0 to 3.0.0.RC1 upgrades Kotlin stdlib/reflect from 1.9.25 to 2.1.0, so the native-image failure is more likely metadata/API-related than setup-related.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0e36d946e4e277d9016a418a33719c8197922010ffbcbee4e1\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1114, "output": 438, "cacheRead": 33792, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 35344, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782680110670, "responseId": "resp_0e36d946e4e277d9016a418a2f419c8197a8c8620eca69631c"}, "toolResults": []}
